                                                                <https://w3id.org/narn/social/wasTheKingOf>
                                                              ) ;
                                       rdfs:comment "Character lived in a place during some period."@en ;
                                       rdfs:label "lived in"@en ;
                                       <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "dwelt in"@en .


###  https://w3id.org/narn/social/loved
<https://w3id.org/narn/social/loved> rdf:type owl:ObjectProperty ;
                                     rdfs:subPropertyOf <https://w3id.org/narn/social/hasEmotionalRelationWith> ;
                                     rdfs:comment "Character had feelings of love towards another."@en ;
                                     rdfs:label "loved"@en ;
                                     <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "had love for"@en .


###  https://w3id.org/narn/social/mutuallyLoved
